Title: Jaipur
Description: The multi award-winning game Jaipur, by sebastien pauchon, returns with all new artwork by Vincent Dutrait and the same great game play. Players take on the roles of two of the city's most powerful traders seeking to earn their invite to the maharaja?s court. Blending strategy and luck, Jaipur is a fast-paced card game that is easy to learn while offering plenty of depth to dedicated players. The new Edition of Jaipur is the first game to kick off space cowboy new 2-player collection. The first print run of Jaipur features an exclusive metallic collectible coin to determine the first player!
